trans-unit.source: Contains configuration elements for the NetTcpPortSharing sharing service.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder konfigurasjonen elementer for NetTcpPortSharing deling av tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The NET.TCP Port Sharing Service allows multiple processes to share the same TCP port.
trans-unit.target: På NETTET. TCP-Port Sharing Service gjør flere prosesser til å dele samme TCP-porten.

trans-unit.source: This class contains properties that configure this service.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen inneholder egenskaper som konfigurerer denne tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activation.Configuration.NetTcpSection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activation.Configuration.NetTcpSection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the user accounts for processes that host [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] services and are granted connection access to the sharing service.
trans-unit.target: Henter brukerkontoene for prosesser som er vert for [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] tjenester og tilgang tilkoblingen til tjenesten deling.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activation.Configuration.SecurityIdentifierElementCollection"></xref> that contains user accounts for processes that host [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] services and are granted connection access to the sharing service.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activation.Configuration.SecurityIdentifierElementCollection"> </xref> som inneholder brukerkontoer for prosesser som er vert for [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] tjenester og tilgang tilkoblingen til tjenesten deling.

trans-unit.source: The default values returned are LocalSystem, Admin, NS, LS, and IIS_USRS.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdier returnerte er LocalSystem, Admin, NS, LS og IIS_USRS.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the maximum outstanding connections that are accepted from the shared connection, but are not yet dispatched to [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] services.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir det maksimale antallet utestående tilkoblinger som godtas fra den delte tilkoblingen, men ennå ikke fordele til [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] services.

trans-unit.source: The maximum outstanding connections that are accepted from the shared connection, but are not yet dispatched to [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Det maksimale antallet utestående tilkoblinger som godtas fra den delte tilkoblingen, men ennå ikke fordele til [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The default is 10.
trans-unit.target: Standard er 10.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the maximum outstanding concurrent accepting threads on the listening endpoint for the sharing service.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir de maksimale utestående samtidige godtar trådene lytting endepunktet for tjenesten deling.

trans-unit.source: The maximum outstanding concurrent accepting threads on the listening endpoint for the sharing service.
trans-unit.target: De utestående samtidige godtar maksimumstråder på lytting sluttpunktet for tjenesten deling.

trans-unit.source: The default is 2.
trans-unit.target: Standard er 2.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the maximum number of pending connections for this sharing service.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir det maksimale antallet ventende tilkoblinger til denne tjenesten for deling.

trans-unit.source: The default value is 100.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er 100.

trans-unit.source: The maximum number of pending connections for this sharing service.
trans-unit.target: Maksimalt antall ventende tilkoblinger for deling tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the timeout for the NetTcpPortSharing sharing service.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir tidsavbruddet for NetTcpPortSharing deling av tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: This property specifies the timeout for reading the framing data and performing connection dispatching from the underlying connections.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen angir tidsavbruddet for lesing av data for rammeverk og utføre tilkoblingen sending fra de underliggende tilkoblingene.

trans-unit.source: The default is 10 seconds.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er 10 sekunder.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a Boolean value that indicates whether the port sharing service uses Microsoft Teredo service to listen on TCP ports on behalf of [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] services.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en boolsk verdi som indikerer om porten deling tjenesten bruker Microsoft Teredo-tjenesten ikke lytte på TCP-port på vegne av [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] services.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the port sharing service uses Microsoft Teredo service to listen on TCP ports on behalf of [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] services; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis porten deling tjenesten bruker Microsoft Teredo-tjenesten ikke lytte på TCP-port på vegne av [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] services; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
